      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STOCKHOLM (3) proven miler in career best form. Back in trip from the good gate when he demolished a handy field over 1400m at this track. Went under narrowly in the Parkes Cup over this trip two-back and should prove too good for these. BLACKLIST (2) kept fresh after struggling in town over the staying trips at his last two outings. Can stalk the speed and score a long overdue victory. LIKE LUKEY (6) performed above expectations when he swooped late to score a solid win over 1600m at Warren with the 59.5kg. Looks up to this class and has each way prospects. SHADOW DANE (4) fitter after two runs back and gets weight relief today after failing to threaten when sixth over 1400m at this track. Maps well and not to be overlooked. JUST ON FIRE (9) goes well at this track and trip and throw into the exotics.",
